title: Pregnant Sam Faiers squeezes baby bump into figure-hugging nude dress
text:
Submit Sam Faiers is making pregnancy look easy as she nails yet another fabulous maternity look. The former TOWIE star, 24, shared a new selfie with her 1.4million Instagram followers on Saturday (17 October) and looked every inch the blooming mum-to-be. 
© Instagram / samanthafaiers1 And, believe it or not, she isn't even wearing a maternity dress!In fact, the reality TV star - who is six months pregnant - squeezed herself into a clinging, baby-bump hugging dress from her own shop, Minnie's Boutique.After posting the photo of herself wearing a stylish nude/beige frock, Sam wrote: "Who said I couldn't squeeze myself into @minniesboutique Autumn/winter dress haha. Get this suzie beige dress online now £36."And we think Sam looks gorgeous. 
© Instagram / samanthafaiers1 Fans were quick to agree, with one saying: "Wish I could look that amazing pregnant/not pregnant lol."Another gushed: "What a beautiful figure."
